Package controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComputerPlayer
    Computer player class for playing the game according to a strategy.
    Game
    Class for controlling a Spectrangle game.
    HumanPlayer
    Human player controller for the game, mostly validating input from the console and parsing this to a move that is readable by the game.
    MarionettePlayer
    Marionette player is a class used by the server and the Client to keep track of players from connected Clients.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidIndexException
    Exception for indexes outside the board.
    InvalidMoveException
    Exception for constructing moves using the wrong constructor.
